column3: This is a lot of tasks. I want to be able to add a lot of text here and split it up across lines in a readable manner, so I'll try testing this multiline usage later. For right now, this is going to look a little sloppy when printed back but that's ok.
This was a task I never took care of from a long time ago and I'm glad I didn't, it was a shitty job and someone had to do it. It just didn't have to be me, thank god.
Damn boi popped out in a flash!
